text-right\">\n                      {item.value}\n                    </span>\n                  </div>\n                ))}\n              </div>\n\n              <div className=\"pt-2 text-center text-[10px] font-mono text-white/30\">\n                UEN: 202621347N • REGISTERED IN SINGAPORE\n              </div>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Bento Grid highlighting Core Divisions */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-16 lg:pb-24 border-t border-white/5 pt-16\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"text-center max-w-[800px] mx-auto mb-16\">\n            <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#009DFF] uppercase font-bold\">\n              Operational Structures\n            </span>\n            <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[34px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n              Our Organizational Divisions\n            </h2>\n            <p className=\"text-[14px] text-white/60 font-light mt-3\">\n              We coordinate engineering excellence across specialized entities designed for rigorous development.\n            </p>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n            {highlights.map((item, idx) => (\n              <div\n                key={idx}\n                className=\"p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-white/5 bg-[#030304]/40 hover:border-[#009DFF]/20 transition-all flex flex-col justify-between group\"\n              >\n                <div className=\"space-y-4\">\n                  <div className=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center group-hover:border-[#009DFF]/45 transition-colors\">\n                    {item.icon}\n                  </div>\n                  <h3 className=\"text-[19px] font-semibold text-white tracking-tight\">\n                    {item.title}\n                  </h3>\n                  <p className=\"text-[13.5px] leading-[1.6] text-white/60 font-light font-sans\">\n                    {item.desc}\n                  </p>\n                </div>\n                <div className=\"mt-8 pt-4 border-t border-white/5 flex items-center justify-between text-[11px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider\">\n                  <span>Authorized Division</span>\n                  <CheckCircle2 className=\"w-3.5 h-3.5\" />\n                </div>\n              </div>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Operating Model Interactive Showcase */}\n      <section className=\"relative w-full px-6 lg:px-16 pb-16 lg:pb-24 border-t border-white/5 pt-16\">\n        <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto\">\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center\">\n            <div className=\"lg:col-span-5\">\n              <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-[0.2em] text-[#E4000F] uppercase font-bold\">\n                Operating Model\n              </span>\n              <h2 className=\"text-[28px] sm:text-[34px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight mt-2\">\n                The Garage, Foundry, & Factory Process\n              </h2>\n              <p className=\"text-[14.5px] text-white/75 mt-4 font-light leading-[1.6]\">\n                Our signature system defines how we execute enterprise automation, assuring strict controls, security guidelines, and compliance boundaries.\n              </p>\n\n              <div className=\"space-y-4 mt-6\">\n                <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#050505]/60 flex items-start gap-4\">\n                  <div className=\"text-[13px] font-mono text-[#E4000F] px-2.5 py-1 rounded bg-[#E4000F]/10 border border-[#E4000F]/20 font-bold shrink-0\">\n                    01\n                  </div>\n                  <div>\n                    <h4 className=\"text-[15px] font-s